- We have a good eye. 
 - You can leave.

29
00:02:13,456 --> 00:02:15,576
Wasn't it you who said...

30
00:02:16,296 --> 00:02:19,216
Fine. Call me if you need anything.

31
00:02:19,216 --> 00:02:22,056
- Thanks. Bye. 
 - Bye.

32
00:02:22,056 --> 00:02:25,356
So handsome. He's the man who was in the toilet just now, right?

33
00:02:25,356 --> 00:02:27,256
That's him.

34
00:02:30,056 --> 00:02:34,596
You sent Mai Mai to distract Cheng Kai Ran. How were you so sure it’d work?

35
00:02:34,596 --> 00:02:37,796
I just know Mr. Cheng.

36
00:02:38,516 --> 00:02:43,076
You're not just a good actor. You also know people and are smart.

37
00:02:43,076 --> 00:02:44,976
What did you want to see me about?

38
00:02:45,996 --> 00:02:49,056
I came to apologize. About Jiang Lu Zhi, I...

39
00:02:49,056 --> 00:02:51,776
Okay. Anything else?

40
